      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Time To Arise</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Wasting all the summer, </l>
          <l>Smoking pot, drinking wine, having fun. </l>
          <l>So please forgive me for being silly, </l>
          <l>'Cause I don't want to be calm, in control in time. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>'Cause it's the time to arise, </l>
          <l>Like a never aging child, </l>
          <l>Put your mind off the line, </l>
          <l>Just this summer. </l>
          <l>'Cause it's the time to arise, </l>
          <l>Let the future wait awhile, </l>
          <l>Put good life on the line, </l>
          <l>Just this summer. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>What the rush, there would be more summers, </l>
          <l>You may ask, but I'll say only that, </l>
          <l>I'm saying goodbye my friends, I'm not leaving yet, </l>
          <l>But goodbye, is to leave memories of you behind. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>'Cause it's the time to arise…</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
